==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪpə(r)|-aɪpə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{US}} (''Canada'') An [[absorbent]] [[garment]] worn by a [[baby]] who does not yet have [[voluntary]] control of his or her [[bladder]] and/or [[bowels]] or by someone who is [[incontinent]].
#{{British}} a [[diamond]] shaped [[pattern]], either woven into cloth or made on a wall using bricks

====Synonyms====
*{{UK}} {{archaic}} [[napkin]] 
*{{UK}} {{AU}} [[nappy]]

